<body style="color: #111827; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px 0px">
  <div
    style="
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    "
  >
    <div style="background-color: #16a34a; color: #ffffff; text-align: center; padding: 20px">
      <h1 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0"><%= subject %></h1>
    </div>

    <div style="padding: 20px">
      <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.6">
        We’re thrilled to have you join <strong>Calo Football Online Manager</strong>! You’ve just taken the first step towards building your dream
        football team and climbing to the top of the manager’s leaderboard.
      </p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 12px">Here’s what’s waiting for you:</h3>
      <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; list-style-type: disc">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.6"><strong>$5,000,000</strong> transfer budget to exchange and enhance your team.</li>
        <li style="line-height: 1.6">
          A squad of <strong>20 talented players</strong>:
          <ul style="margin: 8px 0 0 20px; padding-left: 20px; list-style-type: circle">
            <li>3 Goalkeepers</li>
            <li>6 Defenders</li>
            <li>6 Midfielders</li>
            <li>5 Attackers</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top: 24px; line-height: 1.6">
        Use your budget wisely, scout new talent, and strategically manage your squad to lead them to glory.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #e5e7eb; color: #374151; text-align: center; padding: 16px">
      <p style="margin: 0; line-height: 1.6">Best regards,</p>
      <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #16a34a">The Calo Football Online Manager Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
